11
00:01:33,220 --> 00:01:37,980
=Turbulent Love=

12
00:01:38,100 --> 00:01:42,340
=Episode 16=
=Lost in Translation=

13
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,320
It's all my fault.

14
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,560
When we were looking into Yu...

15
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:28,830
I mean, Miss Hao.

16
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,000
Whenever things got fishy,

17
00:04:33,190 --> 00:04:34,270
I always told you to trust her.

18
00:04:36,750 --> 00:04:38,560
I only listened to you

19
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:45,390
