20
00:04:53,870 --> 00:04:55,190
Here's the problem.

21
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,800
We could've gone abroad after the deal,

22
00:04:58,600 --> 00:05:00,160
but Liang Zhaokun used your name

23
