to sign deals with the councilman.

24
00:05:04,750 --> 00:05:06,120
They're grooming a new player.

25
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:09,160
Now they won't let us walk away,

26
00:05:10,950 --> 00:05:12,270
and they'll trip us at every turn.

27
00:05:15,830 --> 00:05:17,040
Miss Zhu sent gifts over

28
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,070
on behalf of her godfather.

29
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:19,960
They're hoping

30
00:05:20,950 --> 00:05:21,790
