- I bought some.

47
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:34,780
She won't touch it.

48
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:36,430
Takeout never tastes the same.

49
00:06:38,190 --> 00:06:39,720
Have the wonton shop cooks

50
00:06:40,390 --> 00:06:41,430
