53
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:48,360
Spare no expense or effort.

54
00:06:48,390 --> 00:06:49,360
Whatever it takes.

55
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:50,510
Got it?

56
00:06:50,630 --> 00:06:51,480
Zhijie...

57
00:06:59,190 --> 00:07:01,390
