65
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,360
No scallions, no cilantro.

66
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:01,590
Have a try.

67
00:08:01,830 --> 00:08:02,670
Just try it.

68
00:08:12,270 --> 00:08:13,110
It's too stuffy in here.

69
00:08:13,950 --> 00:08:15,390
Let's go to a place you like.

70
00:08:33,670 --> 00:08:34,510
Hao Yu,

71
00:08:35,670 --> 00:08:37,030
