93
00:11:12,750 --> 00:11:13,590
Hao Yu,

94
00:11:15,870 --> 00:11:16,720
I promise you.

95
00:11:17,510 --> 00:11:18,910
I won't lock you up, scold you,

96
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,480
or take your phone away.

97
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:23,790
I'll never do that again.

98
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:26,910
And I won't ask

99
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:28,960
