100
00:11:30,550 --> 00:11:32,080
I won't bring up anything from the past.

101
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:34,390
No one in this world will ever bring that up.

102
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,870
Let's take nothing has ever happened.

103
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:40,670
It never happened. Okay?

104
00:11:47,550 --> 00:11:48,390
I can't.

105
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:59,750
Since the day we met,

106
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:03,440
