107
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:09,920
Hao Yu,

108
00:12:10,870 --> 00:12:11,790
we'll go to the UK tomorrow...

109
00:12:11,790 --> 00:12:13,240
I got close to you and become

110
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:14,360
- We'll go tomorrow.
- your girlfriend...

111
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:16,510
- We can go now.
- Your girlfriend...

112
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:18,550
