- I was just using you.

113
00:12:18,670 --> 00:12:19,600
Then we'll get married.

114
00:12:19,630 --> 00:12:20,510
To take down Cangfeng.

115
00:12:20,510 --> 00:12:21,510
You can have any kind

116
