163
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:32,270
Too many lies and too much hatred
stood in our way.

164
00:14:34,270 --> 00:14:35,120
I beg you.

165
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:37,670
Please let me go.

166
00:14:38,440 --> 00:14:40,120
Or just kill me, okay?

167
00:14:40,240 --> 00:14:41,360
