219
00:17:28,240 --> 00:17:29,080
Hao Yu.

220
00:17:30,480 --> 00:17:32,030
Hao Yu, lie to me one more time, okay?

221
00:17:32,310 --> 00:17:33,720
Lie to me one more time, okay?

222
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:35,440
