237
00:22:04,110 --> 00:22:06,000
Too many lies stood in our way-

238
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:07,680
Suspicion, and hatred.

239
00:22:09,160 --> 00:22:10,000
Your lives

240
00:22:11,110 --> 00:22:13,110
