244
00:22:20,310 --> 00:22:21,550
From the very beginning,

245
00:22:23,920 --> 00:22:24,960
you were wrong.

246
00:22:26,030 --> 00:22:26,920
Dead wrong!

247
00:22:29,640 --> 00:22:30,750
You said he turned you into

248
00:22:30,790 --> 00:22:31,960
someone who doesn't know love.

249
00:22:33,110 --> 00:22:34,790
Do you think you're any different

250
00:22:36,510 --> 00:22:38,160
from Liang Zhaokun right now?

251
00:22:38,750 --> 00:22:40,440
When I adopted you,

252
00:22:41,310 --> 00:22:42,480
I meant to raise you

253
00:22:42,680 --> 00:22:44,160
