254
00:22:44,720 --> 00:22:46,400
But everything went wrong.

255
00:22:46,790 --> 00:22:48,110
Love isn't forcing,

256
00:22:49,790 --> 00:22:51,720
controlling, or possessing.

257
00:22:52,270 --> 00:22:53,440
Love is about respect

258
00:22:54,960 --> 00:22:56,030
and fulfillment.

259
00:22:56,480 --> 00:22:58,550
What do you want me to fulfill?

260
00:22:59,000 --> 00:22:59,840
Hao Yu?

261
00:23:00,550 --> 00:23:01,640
What do you want?

262
00:23:02,830 --> 00:23:04,000
Turn myself in right now,

263
00:23:04,590 --> 00:23:06,350
