274
00:23:51,690 --> 00:23:55,660
♪Obsession and sober, I'm torn in two♪

275
00:23:55,850 --> 00:23:59,570
♪If I could still♪

276
00:23:59,970 --> 00:24:02,640
♪Be entangled with you♪

277
00:24:02,840 --> 00:24:06,290
♪Let me stay in your rainy days♪

278
00:24:06,910 --> 00:24:10,970
♪Unaware of the changing seasons♪

279
00:24:10,970 --> 00:24:13,780
♪With eyes closed♪

280
00:24:13,780 --> 00:24:17,770
♪Your hate or lies♪

281
00:24:17,920 --> 00:24:23,620
♪I take it all as love♪

