297
00:26:45,240 --> 00:26:46,350
You're not going to the UK.

298
00:26:47,720 --> 00:26:49,750
I won't indulge or spoil you anymore.

299
00:26:52,030 --> 00:26:53,480
I want you to live and pay

300
